'''Aɣṛab n Berlin''' (S [[Tutlayt Talmant|Telmant]]: ''Berliner Mauer'') yella d aɣṛab ɣezzifen ibeṭṭu [[Berlin]] ar sin n izegnan (asemran d utrim) d tamiwin i d-yezzin deg  [[Tagduda Tamegdayt n Talmant|Lalman tasemrant]]. Iswi deg tmuski-ynes (lebni-ynes) d asersi n tilas n tukkit gar n Berlin d Lalman tasemrant. Tamuski-ynes tessenta (lebni-ynes yebda) deg wass n [[13 ɣuct]] [[1961]]. Dɣa yettwasses (yettusejhed) aṭas n tikwal maca yeldi deg wass n [[9 wamber]] [[1989]] sin akin yettwadrem s talɣa tazun-midt.<ref>{{amnir n web| akala = https://d-nb.info/gnd/4094837-7 | azwel = isalan ɣef weɣṛab n Berlin deg tansa d-nb.info | anefsar = d-nb.info|akala n ufaylu= https://web.archive.org/web/20191209121527/https://d-nb.info/gnd/4094837-7|azmez n ufaylu=2019-12-09}}</ref><ref>{{amnir n web| akala = https://catalogue.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/cb119380937 | azwel = isalan ɣef weɣṛab n Berlin deg tansa catalogue.bnf.fr | anefsar = catalogue.bnf.fr| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502210054/https://catalogue.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/cb119380937 | azmez n ufaylu = 2 mayu 2019 }}</ref><ref>{{amnir n web| akala = https://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh85013357 | azwel = isalan ɣef weɣṛab n Berlin deg tansa id.loc.gov | anefsar = id.loc.gov|akala n ufaylu= https://web.archive.org/web/20191209121531/https://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh85013357|azmez n ufaylu=2019-12-09}}</ref>
Azal n 3,5 n imelyan seg Lalman tasemrant sizdwen ɣef tkerfiwin n yinig id yettusefken seg tkura tasemrant send n usbeddi n weɣṛab d beṭṭu ɣef Lalman Tamegdayt anda aṭas deg-sen zegren tilisa gar n Berlin tasemrant ar Berlin tutrimt acki syinna zemren ad inigen ar Lalman tutrimt d tmura n [[Turuft|Uruppa]] tutrimin niden. Aɣṛab-a amzun (meḥsub) yegdel yall talɣiwin n yinig. Gar n iseggasen n [[1961]] d [[1989]] azal n 100,000 n yimdanen urmen (ɛerḍen) ad rewlen seg Berlin tasemrant dɣa ugar n 5000 deg-sen ssawṭen ad rewlen sufell n weɣṛab deg wakud anda i yukksen (mmuten) gar n 136 ar ugar n 200 deg-sen.<ref name="cnn.com">{{amnir n web
